reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars 18" leaf might not fit
reviews.reviewText: I ordered the 20" size bag based on representations in the description that it would fit an 18" leaf. My 18" table leafs have skirting on both sides and the 20" bag would not fit my 18" leaf. If the table leaf did not have the skirting, the 20" bag would have been fine. Otherwise, I was pleased with the product. I returned the 20" size and ordered the larger 24" size.
